  "description": [
    "THIRD PART F SPARROW STILL ON HAND Mrs Grose Seems to Have an Assort ment of Husbands Mrs Nellie Grose of Harrisburg Pa but formerly of Henrico county comtin ues to write miseives to her supposed husband John Grose letters con cerning her have also been received from other parties seeming to indicate that she has another husband on hand besides Evarts and Grose She was divorced from the former as stated in yesterdays Tunes on December th last and married Grose on the 20h A man named Sparrow who alleges that she is his wife is still on hand and he asserts in a letter that she has never been divorced from him Mrs Grose has written a letter in which she says that she never autho rized the lis pendens placed on the prop erty of Mr Grose which prevents him rom disposing of the same She is ex ted to arrive here L0morrow A small child of Mr Holloway who lives near Howards Grove was quite painfully hurt yesterday The little boy was wrestling with another child and fell and wrenched his shoulder Dr J Travis Taylor was summoned and renederd medical attention No bones were broken"
  ],
